-- Mexichem May Complete Deals to Acquire Two Companies Soon
-- B y   C a r l o s   M a n u e l   R o d r i g u e z
-- 2012-10-26T19:20:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-26/mexichem-may-complete-deals-to-acquire-two-companies-soon.html
Mexichem SAB, the chemical maker
that has bought more than 15 companies since 2007, may land two
more acquisitions as soon as this quarter, an executive said.  Reaching an agreement on both transactions, one in the U.S.
and one in  South America , is not certain, Ricardo Gutierrez,
president of the company’s executive committee, said today in an
interview in Mexico City. “We’re competing with other companies
to complete the acquisitions,” he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Charles Siler at 
 csiler@bloomberg.net  